# {{lb|fr|emphatic}} [[themselves]]

====Usage notes====
* Emphatic reflexive pronouns are used for extra emphasis where they are not grammatically required:
*: {{uxi|fr|elle l'a vu|t=she saw it}}
*: {{uxi|fr|elle l'a vu '''elle-même'''|t=she saw it herself}}
* ''{{lang|fr|elles-mêmes}}'' is used for groups of all females or groups of nouns of all feminine gender
